Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:05.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:09.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,È stata lei il primo amore di Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La villa va a fuoco!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.49,0:24:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non può essere!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma lì dentro... Lì c'è ancora...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.41,0:24:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami è ancora lì!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami!
